templateVersions.content:
Analyze this student enrollment and determine: 1. Probability of successful admission, based on {!$Input:studentEnrollment.AI_Priority_Score__c} (a score from 0–100, where 80 or above indicates High Priority per existing org automation) and {!$Input:studentEnrollment.Enrollment_Status__c} 
2. Financial risk based on the discount applied: {!$Input:studentEnrollment.Discount_Percentage__c}% against the course fee {!$Input:studentEnrollment.Course__r.Course_Fee__c}
3. Overall enrollment health: classify as Low, Medium, or High Risk 
4. A recommendation: Approve or Reject, with a one-sentence justification
